where we talk
about why you might

00:45:06.070 --> 00:45:08.410
want to watch this with
questions and not with simply

00:45:08.410 --> 00:45:09.315
applause.

00:45:09.315 --> 00:45:10.690
But yeah, that's
a great example,

00:45:10.690 --> 00:45:12.150
and I'm glad you raised it.

00:45:12.150 --> 00:45:12.825
So thanks.

00:45:12.825 --> 00:45:14.200
And thanks for
coming, everybody.

00:45:14.200 --> 00:45:15.227
It's very nice of you.

00:45:15.227 --> 00:45:16.060
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:45:16.060 --> 00:45:17.130
AUDIENCE: So it
seems like this is

00:45:17.130 --> 00:45:19.254
sort of an interesting and
